<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV60">
<l>mulaiyō muḻumuṟṟum pōntila moypūṅ kuḻalkuṟiya</l>
<l>kalaiyō varaiyillai nāvō kuḻaṟuṅ kaṭalmaṇṇellām</l>
<l>vilaiyō veṉamiḷi ruṅkaṇ ṇivaḷpara mēperumāṉ</l>
<l>malaiyō tiruvēṅ kaṭameṉṟu kaṟkiṉṟa vācakamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Her] breasts, they are not [yet] fully grown. [Her] curls bear signs of covering flowers.</l>
<l>[Her] girdle, it is not on [her] waist. [Her] tongue, it babbles. [Her] eyes sparkle:</l>
<l>“do they have a price on all the sea[-bordered] earth?” Highest to her</l>
<l>are the words she learns: “The great lord’s mountain, it is Tiruvēṅkaṭam.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
